This is an island themed lila_panic map i made awhile back, its currently a v1, which is my only version since my computer is crap, i had to get someone to compile for me, who i don't talk to much anymore. If anyone out there has a decent computer and can compile this map again for me, i can easily work out a newer version.

Known Bugs:
- When starting the boat, it sometimes kills players inside of it when exiting the dock, once its away from the dock, its fine.

Hopefully ill get some more maps up in the future, hope ya'll like it!
